D. TRADEMARK NOTICE
----------------------------------------------------------------

Enqpy™, EnqpyADS™, Enqpy™-Certified, and Security, Settled.™
are trademarks of Enqpy™ Foundation Inc., a Delaware nonstock
nonprofit corporation, licensed to NQP LLC under the Foundation–NQP
IP License Agreement.

The Covenant frees the patent; it does not free the marks. Trademark
use in derivative work or implementation is governed by the Foundation
Trademark Use Guidelines. In particular:

  - A conforming implementation may state that it is "Reference-
    Compatible with the Enqpy™ reference implementation," or "based on
    the Enqpy™ reference implementation," with appropriate attribution
    and a link to this repository, and should carry its own project
    name (not a name that places the Enqpy™ mark in the project's
    name).

  - A fork or derivative work may not be presented as the Enqpy™
    implementation, as Enqpy™-Certified, or as Enqpy™-Compatible
    without separate Foundation conformance certification and
    trademark licensing.

  - Citation use of the marks for academic, journalistic, or
    educational purposes is permitted under standard nominative
    fair-use principles, provided attribution is clear and
    endorsement is not suggested.

